### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### LOGIN
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}